column3: Not sure if you should merge yet, if @cozz meta-data change get's merged we will have new strings, the same goes for the -dbcache pull or my little .ui cleanup.\n

Almost every merged pull brings string changes. It's never a good time...

If only there wasn't all the `<location line="-141"/>` diff noise every time for messages that didn't change at all, it'd make sense to do this much more often.
